Reading Unicorn companies list

The full and updated list of Unicorn companies used on this analysis can be found here, at the CBInsights website.

library(readxl)
library(echarts4r)
library(reactable)

unicorn_data <- readxl::read_excel("unicorn_companies.xlsx", skip = 2)
reactable(unicorn_data)
